bBWVIx-s6.memHandModelNotes:
In addition to PMUs, include edge pixels at forest/urban ecotone's also (selected AMUs).  Amy Silvano 6jun05

Removed hand model for this species and "forest/open ecotone only" selection in edge type (had no ecotone width specified). Model is captured using PMU/AMUs with 120m buffer. MJR 11 October 2007.
